Description: This package makes it easy to install and load all packages and functions used in 
  CourseKata courses. It additionally provides a handful of helper functions and augments some 
  generic functions to provide cohesion between the network of packages. Learn more about CourseKata 
  at <https://www.coursekata.org>.
URL: https://www.github.com/UCLTALL/coursekata-r
